,自從facebook變左睇唔到朋友動態之後就已經未落,通常一開波玩得fb既人都係upload相,句子,等人留言傾計,仲記得以前一講左句野上FB,D朋友就一齊係果到吹水,十足十MSN咁,依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔禁落去人地果板都睇唔到,全部睇廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIg都on99啦 變左跟瀏覽興趣show有關既post之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nig 最on9係唔跟時間show post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時我個fd岩岩 post完野轆極都冇但可以見到d 大page兩日前既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nfb都係咁而且仲有仆街嘢<br />\n試過打完風嗰日喺個wall見到第一個post寫住颱風預計後日吹襲香港<br />\n心諗乜而家啲風打得咁密個刻，望望個upload time<br />\n屌佢原來係前日啲post<br />\n<br />\n而且有時見有啲link得意撳咗入去睇<br />\n屌佢條仆街之後幾日都喺個wall見到同一個專頁嘅post中出十連發咁狂推上嚟<br />\n其他post就唔見晒<br />\n<br />\n而且朋友又唔多update，就算update都已經俾唔同廣告同專頁嘅post淹沒咗，或者淨係推啲我like過一兩次嘅朋友post出嚟，load十年都係嗰堆內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有而家fb個撚個都偽善撚，搞到有時有啲嘢想寫下都唔敢post，廢撚事俾人批鬥<br />\n<br />\n所以最後頂唔撚順deactivate咗個account算數，手機就disable個app佢（如果唔係入面有成堆以前up落嘅相，我晨早delete account添呀）"},{"pid":"0e01ca784acf92f49b03c4160012d2fc6e47dc8e","tid":458651,"uid":17232,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:02:27.000Z","msg":"Facebook花五年時間摧毀Snapchat? 咪笑撚死啦，snapchat摧毀facebook就差唔多，facebool抄返黎個story有人用架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f4e4937d57f83d3438cbab0eb4b04db8de2328","tid":458651,"uid":78900,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:04:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解呢排開始忽然出現d黑facebook文？</blockquote><br />\n民國復興 = 夢醒時份 <br />\n五毛撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i