<br />\n<br />\n希望將來香港能夠有多些推特用戶（包括各大機構及政府部門），將意見自由地發表。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/1395/twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F1395%2Ftwitter&d=AVe2VvwzaJ11tKqN4%2Bn9uP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=437a31f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/1395/twitter</a>"},{"pid":"c2252e3a5bf91ee2cac7430709f4e46de0a99928","tid":458651,"uid":30001,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:53:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇好line<br />\nline喺日本連銀行服務都有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就唔睇好喇<br />\n<br />\n叫過身邊啲friends試下用line，但個撚個都牙痛咁嘅聲<br />\n明明去到朗豪坊個line shop又話啲icon好得意咁爭住影相打卡<br />\n最後得個識日文嘅毒撚friend肯轉會</blockquote><br />\nTelegram喺香港反而得</blockquote><br />\nLine 好耐之前興過一排<br />\n但越黎越多功能但部機又跟唔上，慢左好多<br />\n跟住之後whatsapp An版又話免費<br />\n跟住收左皮lu"},{"pid":"c9a9b85b779339d00ff27507918480e565e702d6","tid":458651,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T13:13:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇好line<br />\nline喺日本連銀行服務都有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就唔睇好喇<br />\n<br />\n叫過身邊啲friends試下用line，但個撚個都牙痛咁嘅聲<br />\n明明去到朗豪坊個line shop又話啲icon好得意咁爭住影相打卡<br />\n最後得個識日文嘅毒撚friend肯轉會</blockquote><br />\nTelegram喺香港反而得</blockquote><br />\nLine 好耐之前興過一排<br />\n但越黎越多功能但部機又跟唔上，慢左好多<br />\n跟住之後whatsapp An版又話免費<br />\n跟住收左皮lu</blockquote><br />\n呃點數, 同比人爆acc 個名臭哂"},{"pid":"6029f5fc7ba1bd03116e3fbb12ff3dc041951611","tid":458651,"uid":838,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T13:14:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇好line<br />\nline喺日本連銀行服務都有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就唔睇好喇<br />\n<br />\n叫過身邊啲friends試下用line，但個撚個都牙痛咁嘅聲<br />\n明明去到朗豪坊個line shop又話啲icon好得意咁爭住影相打卡<br />\n最後得個識日文嘅毒撚friend肯轉會</blockquote><br />\nTelegram喺香港反而得</blockquote><br />\nTelegram最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset